257
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:39,060
To remain internally awake, you can
visualize that part and mentally repeat

258
00:36:39,060 --> 00:36:39,600
it.

259
00:36:48,700 --> 00:36:51,480
Awareness in the right hand thumb.

260
