Fifth toe.

286
00:37:56,000 --> 00:37:58,200
Check that you are internally awake.

287
00:38:02,260 --> 00:38:05,020
Awareness in the left hand thumb.

288
00:38:10,980 --> 00:38:12,080
Index finger.

289
00:38:13,340 --> 00:38:13,720
Middle.

290
00:38:14,420 --> 00:38:15,420
Ring.

291
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:17,720
Little finger.

292
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:22,160
Palm of left hand.

293
00:38:22,420 --> 00:38:23,240
Back of hand.

294
00:38:24,520 --> 00:38:25,600
Wrist.

295
00:38:26,020 --> 00:38:26,580
Forearm.

296
00:38:27,680 --> 00:38:28,240
Elbow.

297
00:38:28,240 --> 00:38:29,420
Upper arm.

298
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:32,740
Shoulder.

