Shin.

305
00:38:46,700 --> 00:38:48,140
Ankle of left foot.

306
00:38:50,620 --> 00:38:51,620
Heel.

307
00:38:53,900 --> 00:38:54,520
Sole.

308
00:38:55,820 --> 00:38:56,960
Top of foot.

309
00:38:58,240 --> 00:38:59,480
Left foot big toe.

310
00:39:01,880 --> 00:39:02,780
Second toe.

311
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:04,540
Third.

312
00:39:05,480 --> 00:39:05,960
Fourth.

313
00:39:06,960 --> 00:39:07,240
Fifth.

314
00:39:08,120 --> 00:39:10,580
Now moving along the back side of the
body.

315
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:17,580
Touch the mind to the heels.

316
00:39:22,700 --> 00:39:23,540
Calves.

317
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,540
Back of knees.

318
00:39:29,160 --> 00:39:31,320
Back of thighs.

319
