Buttocks.

320
00:39:34,920 --> 00:39:35,660
Lower back.

321
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:39,520
Middle back.

322
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,580
Upper back.

323
00:39:44,980 --> 00:39:45,960
Shoulder blades.

324
00:39:47,560 --> 00:39:49,640
Space between the shoulder blades.

325
00:39:51,720 --> 00:39:52,580
Back of neck.

326
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:55,600
Back of head.

327
00:39:58,240 --> 00:40:01,280
The spine from tailbone to back of head.

328
00:40:11,220 --> 00:40:12,520
Crown of head.

329
00:40:15,140 --> 00:40:16,180
Forehead.

330
00:40:17,240 --> 00:40:18,060
Right temple.

331
