696
01:37:15,200 --> 01:37:21,000
And this mental dimension, I invite you to
think of it as the functional mind.

697
01:37:25,080 --> 01:37:29,080
A mind that can be programmed and changed.

698
01:37:31,940 --> 01:37:33,480
Perception, cognition.

699
01:37:37,060 --> 01:37:41,320
A lower intellect, meaning decision
making, pattern recognition.

700
01:37:47,000 --> 01:37:49,940
Memory recollection, memory storage.

701
01:37:55,080 --> 01:38:02,120
And a sense of self that has this idea of,
oh, I am this distinct person.

702
01:38:07,320 --> 01:38:13,080
I have not had the experience of being
confused as someone else.

703
01:38:18,360 --> 01:38:20,620
I'm sure that is possible.

704
01:38:23,240 --> 01:38:30,160
My ego has been healthy in this life to
where I'm contained.

705
01:38:36,580 --> 01:38:50,680
A lot of work is done in the more advanced
branches like bhakti yoga, where there is

706
01:38:50,680 --> 01:38:56,240
the intention to actually dissolve the ego
