708
01:39:05,140 --> 01:39:07,580
That's described as Atma Bhava.

709
01:39:10,220 --> 01:39:16,320
Sometimes in psychic experiences we also
have a sense of shared reality.

710
01:39:25,200 --> 01:39:28,840
But shared ego is more rare as far as I'm
aware.

711
01:39:33,300 --> 01:39:36,780
This here is considered part of the gross
body.

712
01:39:43,940 --> 01:39:52,880
These two, the subtle body, especially in
this area.

713
01:39:53,580 --> 01:39:58,300
A really good example of a subtle body is
the body that you move around in when you

714
01:39:58,300 --> 01:39:58,800
are dreaming.

715
01:40:06,360 --> 01:40:08,220
How many of you remember your dreams?

716
01:40:13,380 --> 01:40:15,300
Maybe half the room, a little more.

717
01:40:15,660 --> 01:40:19,860
How many of you repeatedly remember your
names in your dream?

718
01:40:25,340 --> 01:40:32,060
When's the last time in your dream you
could say definitively, I am Satchitananda

719
01:40:32,060 --> 01:40:32,860
from Nepal?

720
01:40:32,860 --> 01:40:39,820
How many of you could say in your dream,
