721
01:40:40,020 --> 01:40:52,480
And think how many times you repeat that
when you are awake in a normal day.

722
01:40:54,140 --> 01:40:58,520
I find it very hard to remember my name in
dreams.

723
01:40:58,640 --> 01:41:01,980
In fact, when I've tried to do so,
I've come up with other names.

724
01:41:10,520 --> 01:41:11,860
That's why it's subtle.

725
01:41:14,660 --> 01:41:17,600
It has unexpected results, it's harder to
access.

726
01:41:22,620 --> 01:41:27,920
Even making a mental body, for some it may
be easy, for me it's really hard.

727
01:41:28,020 --> 01:41:30,020
I have to construct every single part.

728
01:41:36,640 --> 01:41:38,520
And it never looks like this body.

729
01:41:41,240 --> 01:41:46,500
Then we enter a causal area.

730
01:41:50,940 --> 01:41:55,440
And when I say causal, I want you to
consider what that means for you.

731
01:41:59,220 --> 01:42:01,740
I'm going to use the metaphor of the seed.

732
01:42:05,480 --> 01:42:11,700
If you truly know what type of seed
something is, you can predict the tree or

733
01:42:11,700 --> 01:42:13,600
