734
01:42:18,060 --> 01:42:23,420
The Gyanamaya Kosha contains all the seed
templates in this reality.

735
01:42:31,460 --> 01:42:34,400
The entire physics of the world.

736
01:42:37,960 --> 01:42:43,400
When Newton or the other parallel
discoveries at the same time as him,

737
01:42:47,460 --> 01:42:51,460
